===2000 population===
Agency Village was not counted separately during the [[2000 United States census|2000 Census]].<ref name=ND2000>{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov/prod/cen2000/phc-3-36.pdf |title=Population and Housing Unit Counts, North Dakota |author=U.S. Census Bureau |authorlink=United States Census Bureau |work=2000 Census of Population and Housing |publisher=[[United States Government Publishing Office|Government Printing Office]] |year=2003|access-date=2008-07-20}}</ref> The township reported 277 people, 83 households, and 70 families.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Census 2000 Profiles, Agency Township |url=http://censtats.census.gov/data/SD/0604610900500.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120512151249/http://censtats.census.gov/data/SD/0604610900500.pdf |archive-date=2012-05-12 |website=U.S. Census Bureau}}</ref>

